PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FA rogue trader who took money from
OL,8,Fmultiple victims but did not complete
OL,9,Froofing and renovation work has been
OL,10,Fjailed.
OL,12,FRichard Williams, 53, would fail to
OL,13,Fshow some of the victims' addresses
OL,14,Fonce the majority of the contracted
OL,15,Fprice was paid, according to the
OL,16,Fcouncil.
OL,18,FWhat work was done was of poor quality
OL,19,Fand in many cases needed to be removed
OL,20,Fand re-done. In some cases, money was
OL,21,Ftaken and no work was done at all.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
