FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FThe charges related to 16 separate
OL,8,Fvictims of his fraud, many of whom
OL,9,Fattended court for his hearing. The
OL,10,Ftotal value of the fraud was #75,840.
OL,12,FWilliams, who's from Wimbrick Hey,
OL,13,FWirral, was sentenced to 32 months in
OL,14,Fprison when he appeared at Chester
OL,15,FCrown Court where he was prosecuted
OL,16,Ffor fraud by Cheshire West and Chester
OL,17,FCouncil.
OL,19,FThe offences took place between May
OL,20,F2019 and September 2023 in Cheshire,
OL,21,FMerseyside and Flintshire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAfter the hearing many of Williams'
OL,8,Fvictims commented on his sentencing.
OL,9,FOne said: "He didn't just steal my
OL,10,Fmoney he stole my peace of mind and
OL,11,Fthe dream I was building in my home.
OL,13,F"I have not only lost my money but
OL,14,Fhave had to pay out further money,
OL,15,Fhiring new builders to carry out and
OL,16,Fcomplete the work he never did that
OL,17,Fwas originally agreed."
OL,26,@yD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
