OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FAnother added: "I would like to
OL,8,Fexpress my thanks to Trading Standards
OL,9,Fat Cheshire West and Chester Council
OL,10,Fand to the other victims involved in
OL,11,Fthis case for their courage and
OL,12,Fresilience throughout this long
OL,13,Fprocess while we have waited for
OL,14,Fjustice to be served.
OL,16,F"His actions have completely destroyed
OL,17,Four trust in tradespeople. The
OL,18,Femotional, financial, and practical
OL,19,Feffects of what he did will stay with
OL,20,Fus for a very long time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
