PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,FCouncillor Stuart Bingham said: "I am
OL,8,Freally pleased that our Trading
OL,9,FStandards Officers were able to help
OL,10,Fthese residents get justice.
OL,12,F"The damage done by rogue traders goes
OL,13,Fbeyond money and is a real threat to
OL,14,Ftheir victim's mental and physical
OL,15,Fhealth."
OL,26,@oD@aOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
