CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772727090
OL,3,CRogue trader who took #75,000 from
OL,4,Cvictims for unfinished roofing work
OL,5,Cjailed
OL,7,F"Rogue traders like this face going to
OL,8,Fjail, big fines and compensation
OL,9,Forders. Our Trading Standards Officers
OL,10,Fwork hard to protect residents in
OL,11,FCheshire West and Chester from this
OL,12,Ftype of fraudulent business activity,
OL,13,Fbut they need your help.
OL,15,F"Please report anyone you think may be
OL,16,Fa 'cowboy builder' so that we can
OL,17,Fbring them to justice."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@WO]
